scene.message:
Oishi: Honestly, the Vice{waitkey}{nl}
Principal... the boy may have{nl}
started the fight, but surely{waitkey}{clearbox}he had his reasons. We ought{nl}
to hear him out before we{nl}
pass any judgment...{waitkey}{ret}

Hannya: Outrageous! Taking{nl}
such a defiant attitude with{nl}
me! I'll hear no excuses!{waitkey}{clearbox}It's all lies anyway. As{nl}
punishment: wash the windows,{nl}
copy kanji, and shine{nl}
my shoes!{waitkey}{ret}

Hannya: Ah, if only that{nl}
had been real...{waitkey}{clearbox}Hmph, never mind.{nl}
It's nothing.{nl}
Don't interrupt my writing.{waitkey}{ret}

Hannya: Hey now, quit{nl}
interrupting my writing.{nl}
Or shall you do it too?{waitkey}{ret}

Kiichi: Gimme a break! Why am{nl}
I the only one getting chewed{nl}
out? The prez is guilty too!{waitkey}{clearbox}Yelling without even hearing{nl}
me out - is that what an{nl}
educator does, huh?!{waitkey}{ret}

Kiichi: Pipe down, will ya!{nl}
Why do I gotta copy kanji?!{waitkey}Love. {wait_fr:30}Love. {wait_fr:30}Love.{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Lust. {wait_fr:30}Love{wait_fr:30}......{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Unbelievable. That{nl}
bald geezer's lecturing him{nl}
one-sidedly again.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Kiichi didn't do{nl}
anything wrong... Ayase saw{nl}
it before the school froze.{waitkey}{clearbox}He couldn't stand the prez{nl}
slacking, so he just "gave{nl}
him a little warning." That's{nl}
all!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, hey - don't you{nl}
just wanna smack that bald{nl}
head when you look at it?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Both parties share{nl}
blame. Both should do the{nl}
writing.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Cold logic's bad{nl}
enough, but I really wish{nl}
he'd quit yellin' on emotion.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Grown men acting like{nl}
this... it's not a very{nl}
becoming sight, is it.{waitkey}{ret}
